{"tid":942470,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點同貓系男相處","createTime":"2018-12-15T17:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T19:09:58.000Z","uid":199352,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"27d616c91b9aa5d7911706ef08cc29d86faa3bf2","tid":942470,"uid":199352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T17:45:00.000Z","msg":"好內向 唔識講嘢<br />\n唔識關心人 唔會講自己嘅諗法<br />\n總之就係咩都要估估下<br />\n又傲嬌又高竇又唔笑成日以為佢唔開心 <br />\n<br />\n因為我追佢 我對於呢段關係好小心<br />\n因為覺得 佢都唔係咁鍾意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊左之後 好多時候我都唔敢表達自己嘅諗法<br />\n<br />\n但偏偏我又係好需要人關心嗰種<br />\n其實係有情緒病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 總之間唔中會個人超唔開心<br />\n佢又唔係好識氹我 我就會自己好糾結<br />\n又唔敢同佢講<br />\n<br />\n最慘係佢講嘢仲要1999<br />\n例如今日我問佢可唔可以call佢<br />\n佢答：「但我睇緊電視」<br />\n佢嘅意思係佢睇緊電視好得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係r爆頭"},{"pid":"62e7b70d8f4a39a6082832a4681cf762a89f6689","tid":942470,"uid":431,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T17:45:37.000Z","msg":"同豬系相處"},{"pid":"83b5bfe7de13f96891cbbcbe917830a6f1b2a5cb","tid":942470,"uid":224107,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"62e7b70d8f4a39a6082832a4681cf762a89f6689","tid":942470,"uid":431,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T17:45:37.000Z","msg":"同豬系相處"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T17:46:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19947cc8229751feeb5e8e3146a11566ce6af0da","tid":942470,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T17:47:54.000Z","msg":"豬系女友"},{"pid":"3868b1ad662769587f8d7f76aca8a6056702b1ed","tid":942470,"uid":199352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T17:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喂呀我認真問㗎"},{"pid":"894e49674f6ad5e3238